  imor $p |- ( ( ph -> ps ) <-> ( -. ph \/ ps ) ) $=
    ( wi wn wo pm4.13 birim df-or bitr4 ) ABCADZDZBCJBEAKBAFGJBHI $.
    $([5-Aug-93]$)

  $( Express implication in terms of conjunction.  Theorem 3.4(27) of [Stoll]
